casebody.data:
Traci M. TREAT as Guardian ad Litem for Nadie Ait M'Barek, a minor
v.
Karen ROANE, Veda L. Watson, and Wake Medical Center a/k/a Wakemed. No. 511P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 16, 2006. Charles M. Putterman, Raleigh, for Traci Treat. Christopher G. Smith, Samuel G. Thompson, Raleigh, for Karen Roane. Dan J. McLamb, Raleigh, T. Carlton Younger, III, for Watson & Wake Medical Center.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the conditional petition filed on the 2nd day of October 2006 by Defendant (Karen Roane) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of November 2006."
